ted-Edition-Xbox-360-Picture/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。[[班杰利公司|班杰利公司]]制作了辛普森一家主题的啤酒和甜甜圈口味的冰激琳，所取的名称也和节目有联系<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rutlandherald.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20070719/NEWS04/707190329/1024/NEWS04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012175438/http://www.rutlandherald.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20070719%2FNEWS04%2F707190329%2F1024%2FNEWS04 |archivedate=2013-10-12 |title=Ben & Jerry's delivers Homerific ice cream |accessdate=2014-10-12 |date=2007-07-19 |work=Rutland Herald |author=Gordon Dritschilo |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[Windows_Live_Messenger|Windows Live Messenger]]}}的用户可以免费下载动画和静态图像内容并在与他人聊天时使用<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.dexigner.com/news/11191 | title = Red Box Produce Global Launch Tie-in for the Simpson Movie | accessdate = 2014-10-12 | date = 2007-06-15 | work = Dexigner | archivedate = 2014-07-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140729175925/http://www.dexigner.com/news/11191 }}</ref>。汉堡王发行辛普森一家玩具人偶产品线，随儿童套餐附赠，为此还制作了一系列的辛普森一家主题电视广告加以宣传<ref name="tieins" />。[[捷蓝航空|捷蓝航空]]也举行了系列抽奖活动，获奖者可以前去参加电影在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]举行的[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]。他们还增加了一个《辛普森一家》[[机上娱乐|机上娱乐]]系统的专用频道<ref name="tieins" />。

=== 票房 ===
《辛普森一家大电影》在美国上映的第一天进账3075万8269美元，截至2014年9月，这个成绩可以在历史上的所有电影中排名第53<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/days/?page=open&p.htm | title = Top Single Day Grosses | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141008183537/http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/days/?page=open&p.htm | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | work = Box Office Mojo | publisher = IMDb.com | archivedate = 2014-10-08 }}</ref>。影片首周一共在3922家电影院的5500张银幕上映，进账7403万6787美元并在周末登上票房榜[[冠军|冠军]]宝座<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=30&p=.htm | title = Weekend Box Office July 27–29, 2007 | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | work = Box Office Mojo | archivedate = 2014-10-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009213104/http://boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=30&p=.htm | deadurl = no | publisher = IMDb.com }}</ref>。这也让本片在历史上所有7月开映的电影中首周票房排名第10，并且无论是在不属[[续集|续集]]的电影还是电视节目改编的电影中都是最高的一部<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009214458/http://boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/month/?mo=07&p=.htm | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/month/?mo=07&p=.htm | title = Top Opening Weekends By Month | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | work = Box Office Mojo | archivedate = 2014-10-09 }}</ref>，表现远超出福克斯的4000万美元预期<ref>{{cite news | date = 2007-07-29 | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | work = Reuters | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141010102730/http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/29/us-boxoffice-idUSN2737409820070729 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/29/us-boxoffice-idUSN2737409820070729 | title = "Simpsons" the first family at theaters | author = Dean Goodman | archivedate = 2014-10-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

影片创下多项美国电影票房纪录，如没有采用[[电脑绘图|电脑绘图]]制作的动画电影中首周最高票房纪录，并超越《[[碟中谍2|碟中谍2]]》成为所有根据电视节目改编的电影中首周票房最高的作品；影片的首周票房在所有动画片中排名第3<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20048748,00.html |title=Raking in the d'oh! |author=Joshua Rich |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709075813/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20048748%2C00.html |accessdate=2014-10-10 |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2007-07-30 |archivedate=2014-07-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。电影在71个海外国家和地区上映，第一周就登上国际电影票房冠军宝座，收入达9600万美元，其中单[[英国|英国]]就达2780万美元，是[[二十世纪福克斯|二十世纪福克斯]]公司出品电影在英国首周取得的第二好成绩<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2013-10-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131015104627/http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/30/film-boxoffice-overseas-dc-idUSN2936859520070730 | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/30/film-boxoffice-overseas-dc-idUSN2936859520070730 | title = "Simpsons Movie" rules foreign box office | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | date = 2007-07-29 | author = Frank Segers | work = Reuters | deadurl = no }}</ref>。这个周末英国共有550万观众走进[[电影院|电影院]]，其中观看本片的就超过一半<ref>{{cite news | title = Simpsons film tops record weekend | work = BBC News | date = 2007-07-31 | archivedate = 2014-08-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140810234623/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6923830.stm | deadurl = no | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6923830.stm | accessdate = 2014-10-10 }}</ref>。《辛普森一家大电影》在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]首周进账1320万[[澳大利亚元|澳大利亚元]]，在该国电影史上排名第3，并且是所有动画片中最高的<ref>{{cite news | author = Patrick Kolan | title = Simpsons Movie Breaks Records | work = IGN | date = 2007-07-30 | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/07/31/simpsons-movie-breaks-records | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131014173801/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/07/31/simpsons-movie-breaks-records | archivedate = 2013-10-14 }}</ref>。影片在英国一共进账7842万6654美元，是除美国外的最好成绩，其次则是收入3628万9250美元的[[德国|德国]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=simpsons.htm | title = The Simpsons Movie (2007) International Box office Results | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | work = Box Office Mojo | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140406224127/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=simpsons.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-04-06 }}</ref>。影片在美国和[[加拿大|加拿大]]的上映周期于2007年12月20日结束，共计收入票房1亿8313万5014美元，是2007年美加两国总票房第十二高的电影，也是全球第八高的电影<ref name="box office" />。

