== 反响 ==
=== 专业评价 ===
《辛普森一家大电影》获得了影评人的良好评价。根据[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上收集的200篇评价文章，有180篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”达90%，平均得分7.6（最高10分）<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Flixster | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140907210528/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/simpsons_movie/ | deadurl = no | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/simpsons_movie/ | title = The Simpsons Movie (2007) | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | work = Rotten Tomatoes | archivedate = 2014-09-07 }}</ref>。而{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}上收集的36篇评论中则有35篇好评，无差评，1篇褒贬不一，综合评分80（满分100）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-simpsons-movie | title = Simpsons Movie, The | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | work = Metacritic | archivedate = 2014-08-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140808015600/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-simpsons-movie | publisher = CBS }}</ref>。英国的《[[卫报|卫报]]》和《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》都给予影片四星评价（最高五星）。《泰勒士报》的詹姆斯·波恩（{{lang|en|James Bone}}）表示，《辛普森一家》凭借狡黠的文化指涉和时常闪现的天才赢得了从小娃到文学博士的追棒，电影版也同时做到了这两点<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2011-09-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110906144537/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article2118613.ece | url = http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article2118613.ece | title = The Simpsons Movie – The Times review | accessdate = 2011-09-06 | date = 2007-07-22 | work = The Times | author = James Bone | location = London }}</ref>。彼得·布拉德肖在《卫报》撰文称，影片满足了观众可能会有的任何需求，他还觉得“85分钟时间还远远不足以让17年的喜剧天才走上正义之路”<ref>{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141005100840/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2007/jul/24/animation.family | deadurl = no | url = http://www.theguardian.com/film/2007/jul/24/animation.family | title = The Simpsons Movie | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | date = 2007-07-24 | author = Peter Bradshaw | work = The Guardian | location = London | archivedate = 2014-10-05 }}</ref>。埃德·冈萨雷斯（{{lang|en|Ed Gonzalez}}）称赞了电影中的政治信息，他很喜欢片头的《痒痒鼠与抓抓猫》动画片段，以及随后施瓦辛格总统的处境，还有电影中的视觉噱头<ref name="gonzalez">{{cite news | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110429220549/http://www.slantmagazine.com/film/review/the-simpsons-movie/3004 | url = http://www.slantmagazine.com/film/film_review.asp?ID=3089 | title = The Simpsons Movie | accessdate = 2011-04-29 | date = 2007-07-27 | work = Slant Magazine | author = Ed Gonzalez | archivedate = 2011-04-29 }}</ref>。兰迪·舒尔曼赞扬了演员的配音表现，形容他们把“配音的水准提升到了远超过简单阅读台词的程度”，他特别称赞朱莉·卡夫娜“一定是给出了有史以来最感同身受的表演”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.metroweekly.com/2007/07/homers-odyssey/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141009160022/http://www.metroweekly.com/2007/07/homers-odyssey/ | title = Homer's Odyssey | work = Metro Weekly | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | date = 2007-07-26 | author = Randy Shulman | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-09 }}</ref>。[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]也给予本片正面评价，但他也承认自己“总的来说不是很中意电视动画衍生出的电影”。在他看来，本片“激进的同时又很简单，有颠簸性但心地又很善良，看起来咄咄逼人但并非真要让人感到冒犯”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-simpsons-movie-2007 | title = The Simpsons Movie (PG-13) | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | date = 2007-07-26 | author = Roger Ebert | work = Chicago Sun-Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140830223241/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-simpsons-movie-2007 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-08-30 }}</ref>。《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》的[[理查德·科利斯|理查德·科利斯]]（{{lang|en|Richard Corliss}}）称，影片并没有试图要比电视“更粗鲁或更纠结，而只是规模更大、效果更好”<ref>{{cite news |title=The Simpsons, Bigger and Better |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709143212/http://content.time.com/time/arts/article/0%2C8599%2C1647331%2C00.html |archivedate=2014-07-09 |url=http://content.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1647331,00.html |accessdate=2014-10-10 |author=Richard Corliss |date=2007-07-26 |work=Time }}</ref>。
[[File:Julie_Kavner.jpg|left]]因表演出真挚情感赢得赞誉，她因此还获得了一项[[安妮奖|安妮奖]]提名]]

《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》影评人克劳迪娅·普格（{{lang|en|Claudia Puig}}）认为，电影中的故事的确“值得一部长片电影的时长，这要归功于其中巧妙的剧情和无休止的插科打诨”<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2013-12-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231192917/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2007-07-25-simpsons-review_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/reviews/2007-07-25-simpsons-review_N.htm | title = 'Simpsons' is timely good fun | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | date = 2007-07-26 | work = USA Today | author = Claudia Puig | deadurl = no }}</ref>。帕特里克·科兰认为，本片无疑是继《辛普森一家》的第12季或第13季以来最优秀的《辛普森一家》，他称赞了电影的动画表现，但也觉得片中像[[漫画男|漫画男]]和[[西摩·斯金纳|西摩·斯金纳]]等人物的出场形象太短暂的同时又很无趣<ref>{{cite news | url = http://uk.ign.com/articles/2007/07/26/the-simpsons-movie-au-review | title = The Simpsons Movie AU Review | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141010140316/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/07/26/the-simpsons-movie-au-review | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-10 | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | date = 2007-07-05 | author = Patrick Kolan | work = IGN }}</ref>。柯克·哈尼科特（{{lang|en|Kirk Honeycutt}}）在《[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]》上称颂了电影的善良本性，称其中有着各种程度的笑料，但他也指出，影片在把辛普森一家人带上大银幕的同时，却几乎没有什么进步<ref>{{cite news | title = The Simpsons Movie | date = 2007-07-25 | work = The Hollywood Reporter | author = Kirk Honeycutt}}</ref>。

《[[综艺_(杂志)|综艺]]》的布莱恩·洛瑞（{{lang|en|Brian Lowry}}）称本片虽然“聪明、玩世不恭、讽刺而且应有尽有”，但这些东西“只能勉强”让影片的长度超过电视剧集<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-10-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141010141430/http://variety.com/2007/film/reviews/the-simpsons-movie-1200557648/ | url = http://variety.com/2007/film/reviews/the-simpsons-movie-1200557648/ | title = The Simpsons Movie | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | date = 2007-07-24 | work = Variety | author = Brian Lowry | deadurl = no }}</ref>。丽莎·舒瓦兹鲍姆（{{lang|en|Lisa Schwarzbaum}}）通过《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》称赞了演员的配音表现，但觉得电影中的部分“动作”镜头有些拖泥带水<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20047960,00.html |title=The Simpsons Movie (2007) |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728014720/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20047960%2C00.html |accessdate=2014-10-10 |date=2007-07-24 |author=Lisa Schwarzbaum |work=Entertainment Weekly |archivedate=2014-07-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。斯蒂芬·劳利（{{lang|en|Stephen Rowley}}）将影片与[[电视节目|电视节目]]的早期剧集相比较后总结认为，影片与后期的节目相比表现内容更丰富，但与早期那些让人们如此振奋的节目相比还有很长的路要走<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.cinephobia.com/simpsons.htm | title = The Simpsons Movie (David Silverman), 2007 | accessdate = 2009-09-13 | author = Stephen Rowley | work = Cinephobia.com | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090913222715/http://www.cinephobia.com/simpsons.htm | archivedate = 2009-09-13 }}</ref>。《[[月报_(澳大利亚)|月报]]》杂志（{{lang|en|''The Monthly''}}）影评人[[卢克·戴维斯|卢克·戴维斯]]（{{lang|en|Luke Davies}}）对片长的看法和洛瑞类似，称影片剧情进展速度和半小时的电视剧集相差无几，感觉就像三集电视剧串在一块儿。“我们是在看电影，我们期待会有一些史诗般的东西。”他断言：将来回顾《辛普森一家》的历史时，与其把这部电影视为典范，不如说更象是部不伦不类的怪异作品。<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141010144405/http://www.themonthly.com.au/issue/2007/september/1345705309/luke-davies/ho-diddly-hum?page=0%2C1 | archivedate = 2014-10-10 | title = Ho-Diddly-Hum: David Silverman's "The Simpsons Movie" | url = http://www.themonthly.com.au/issue/2007/september/1345705309/luke-davies/ho-diddly-hum?page=0%2C1 | author = Luke Davies | work = The Monthly }}</ref>

《[[帝国杂志|帝国杂志]]》刊登了一篇较为负面的评价，影评人伊恩·内森（{{lang|en|Ian Nathan}}）将《辛普森一家大电影》和[[可口可乐|可口可乐]]公司推出的失败产品[[新可乐|新可乐]]（{{lang|en|New Coke}}）相提并论，称这是部“完全失败”的电影<ref name="empirereview">{{cite news | url = http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/review.asp?FID=11196 | title = The Simpsons Movie (PG) | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | author = Ian Nathan | work = Empire | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029184058/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/review.asp?FID=11196 }}</ref>。菲尔·维拉利尔（{{lang|en|Phil Villarreal}}）认为，片中“值得一笑的时刻太少”，批评影片“安于现状，没有延伸到新的领域”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.aznightbuzz.com/stories/193320.php | title = 'Simpsons Movie' nothing special | accessdate = 2009-09-12 | date = 2007-07-26 | author = Phil Villarreal | work = Arizona Daily Star | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090912042400/http://www.aznightbuzz.com/stories/193320.php | archivedate = 2009-09-12 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。希拉·约翰斯顿（{{lang|en|Sheila Johnston}}）批评了电影的节奏和其中笑点的水准，仿佛大堆漫画式的笑话堆砌在一起，有些很搞笑，有些则十分勉强<ref>{{cite news |work=The Telegraph |location=London |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080225182853/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml?xml=%2Fnews%2F2007%2F07%2F24%2Fnsimpsons124.xml |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml?xml=/news/2007/07/24/nsimpsons124.xml |title=Review: Big screen stretching it for Simpsons |accessdate=2008-02-25 |date=2007-07-25 |author=Sheila Johnston |archivedate=2008-02-25 }}</ref>。大卫·爱德华兹（{{lang|en|David Edwards}}）也有同样看法，他在评论中写道，影片虽然有“非常优异的半小时节目横冲直撞，但剩下的那些填充内容非常乏味”，他认为这“不算是部很糟糕的电影，只是让人感到非常失望”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/tv-film-news/the-simpsons-movie-493722 | title = Review: The Simpsons Movie | accessdate = 2014-10-10 | date = 2007-07-28 | author = David Edwards | work = Daily Mirror | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140521001641/http://www.mirror.co.uk/tv/tv-news/the-simpsons-movie-493722 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-05-21 }}</ref>。[[科斯莫·兰德斯曼|科斯莫·兰德斯曼]]（{{lang|en|Cosmo Landesman}}）认为，电影中的“幽默似乎失去了那种讽刺和机智”，并且“大部分笑料都是围绕着霍默的愚蠢堆砌起来的”<ref>{{cite news | title = The Simpsons Movie-Sunday Times Review | accessdate = 2007-07-29 | date = 2007-07-29 | author = Cosmo Landesman | work = The Sunday Times | location = London | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110615112148/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/film_reviews/article2141198.ece | archivedate = 2011-06-15 | url = http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/film_reviews/article2141198.ece }}</ref>。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的卡琳娜·绰坎诺（{{lang|en|Carina Chocano}}）也有同样看法，感觉“一旦到达对死亡和意义思考的地步，电影就原型毕露地堕落了。”她把本片于[[1999年电影|1999年]]的《[[南方公园剧场版|南方公园剧场版]]》相比较，该片也改编自电视动画连续剧，绰坎诺称，在冷嘲热讽方面，这两部电影中“没有任何我们每晚在《[[每日秀|每日秀]]》中听不到的东西”<ref>{{cite news | author = Carina Chocano | work = Los Angeles Times | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029204351/http://articles.latimes.com/2007/jul/27/entertainment/et-simpsons27 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2007/jul/27/entertainment/et-simpsons27 | title = Where's the fire? | date = 2007-07-27 | accessdate = 2014-10-11 }}</ref>。布鲁斯·纽曼（{{lang|en|Bruce Newman}}）批评片中大量次要人物的出场仅仅惊鸿一瞥，认为这是一部让人失望的电影<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.mercurynews.com/movies/ci_6461922 | title = Doh! 'Simpsons Movie' is more boohoo than woohoo | accessdate = 2014-10-11 | date = 2007-07-25 | author = Bruce Newman | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029185725/http://www.mercurynews.com/movies/ci_6461922 | work = San Jose Mercury News | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 荣誉 ===
《辛普森一家大电影》赢得了[[英国喜剧奖|英国喜剧奖]]的最佳喜剧电影奖<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140219225818/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7129639.stm | archivedate = 2014-02-19 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7129639.stm | title = British Comedy Awards: winners' list | accessdate = 2014-10-11 | date = 2007-12-06 | work = BBC News }}</ref>和{{lang|en|[[独立电视台|ITV]]}}颁发的首届[[英国国家电影奖|英国国家电影奖]]最佳动画片奖<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7019374.stm | title = Potter wins film awards hat-trick | accessdate = 2014-10-11 | date = 2007-09-28 | author = Fiona Pryor | work = BBC News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141007061256/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/7019374.stm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-10-07 }}</ref>，并在英国[[尼克频道儿童选择奖|尼克频道儿童选择奖]]角逐中击败《[[哈利·波特与凤凰社_(电影)|哈利·波特与凤凰社]]》、《[[加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头|加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头]]》和《[[怪物史莱克3|怪物史莱克3]]》夺得最佳电影奖<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a78143/in-full-nickelodeon-kids-choice-awards-uk-winners.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120825135949/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a78143/in-full-nickelodeon-kids-choice-awards-uk-winners.html | title = In full: Nickelodeon Kids' Choice Awards UK winners | author = Nick Levine | date = 2007-10-20 | accessdate = 2014-10-11 | work = Digital Spy | archivedate = 2012-08-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。电影的预告片在第8届金拖车奖角逐中获得了最佳动画/家庭电影预告片奖<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120319215241/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=20746 | archivedate = 2012-03-19 | url = http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=20746 | title = The 8th Annual Golden Trailer Awards Winners! | accessdate = 2014-10-11 | author = Edward Douglas | date = 2007-05-31 | work = Comingsoon.net }}</ref>。《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》根据票房成绩和{{lang|en|Metacritic}}上的专业评价将本片排在2007年电影的第三位<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.forbes.com/2008/02/19/hollywood-movies-forbesies-biz-media-cx_jb_0220forbesies.html | title = The True Best Pictures Of The Year | accessdate = 2014-10-11 | author = John Burman | date = 2008-02-20 | work = Forbes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140729151839/http://www.forbes.com/2008/02/19/hollywood-movies-forbesies-biz-media-cx_jb_0220forbesies.html | archivedate = 2014-07-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。电影的网站还在第12届[[威比奖|威比奖]]中获得了最佳电影网站奖<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.webbyawards.com/webbys/current.php?season=12#webby_entry_movie | title = Webby Awards '08 Winners | accessdate = 2008-05-19 | work = Webby Awards | archivedate = 2011-04-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110429074337/http://www.webbyawards.com/webbys/current.php?season=12#webby_entry_movie | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

